<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Allwear minorities agree Hicor bid.</title>
<headline>Allwear minorities agree Hicor bid.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Allwear Ltd said on Friday that 90.4 percent of minority shareholders had accepted the offer to buy their shares from parent company Hicor Ltd.</p>
<p>As a result, Allwear's Johannesburg listing will be suspended from the close of business on Friday.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
